# Spaceship-Game-

This is my university course project where I created a text-based, side-scrolling spaceship game. In this game, the user will control a mining ship that collects asteroids.
When the user collects the asteroid less then "50" your score gets increase.

This game was developed in C++ programming languge with use of object oriented programming.

Instructions To Play:-
  "S" MOVE FORWARD
  "W" MOVE UP
  "X" MOVE DOWN
  "A" STAY AT CURRENT POSITION
  "R" SAVE YOUR GAME
  "Q" EXIT

